<ArticleLayout
  title="Vehicle Dynamics Fundamentals | Wavey Dynamics"
  heading="VEHICLE DYNAMICS FUNDAMENTALS"
  subheading="Seminar Series: Vehicle Dynamics Fundamentals"
  image="/images/pages/learn-hero.jpg"
  imagePosition="center"
  description="A comprehensive vehicle dynamics seminar series covering tyres, weight transfer, cornering, suspension, aerodynamics and simulation. Delivered live online by Wavey Dynamics."
>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">We're excited to launch a course focused on the fundamentals of vehicle dynamics for high-performance road and race vehicles.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Designed by people with academic experience and a strong foundation of fluid topics around fundamental concepts; complete spanning the significance of the car, our setting, we want to create a foundation for you to build on and the more advanced topics for your future work and studies.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Having access to a strong base of knowledge from which to build a more solid foundation in the field, you will have the support to continue.</p>

  <p class="mb-10 leading-relaxed">If this course is suitable for you, will help and enable you to remain in vehicle dynamics, it will be a massive accomplishment.</p>

  <h2 class="mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest">What's Covered</h2>

  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start mb-12">
    <div class="flex-1">
      <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">This course is designed to cover all major topics within the field of vehicle dynamics, in a way that's comprehensive but not too dense, so you can comfortably stay engaged with the material throughout. We don't shy away from the physically intuitive.</p>
      <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">Topics covered will include:</p>
      <ul class="wd-list space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
        <li>Tyre Dynamics</li>
        <li>Weight Transfer &amp; Wheel Loading</li>
        <li>Cornering</li>
        <li>Suspension &amp; Kinematics</li>
        <li>Vehicle Aerodynamics</li>
        <li>Modelling &amp; Real-World Vehicle Dynamics</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full md:w-[240px] shrink-0">
      <img src="/images/pages/outreach-seminar.jpg" alt="Vehicle dynamics seminar" class="w-full aspect-[5/4] object-cover" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Who It's For</h2>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">This vehicle dynamics course is best suited to those who have an existing variety of scientific knowledge and want to expand or want to learn more about vehicle dynamics.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">If you still have unanswered questions and you're not sure what's genuinely right for you, here's more about the kind of person it's most suitable to.</p>

  <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">People who:</p>

  <ul class="wd-list mb-12 space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
    <li>are current <strong>university or college students</strong> on an engineering course</li>
    <li><strong>have graduated</strong> with a bachelor's/master's degree in any engineering discipline</li>
    <li>have already <strong>worked or are currently working</strong> in motorsport or another scientific discipline</li>
    <li>are <strong>taking part in or thinking about</strong> a project relevant to vehicle dynamics</li>
    <li>have a <strong>professional engineering background</strong> and are currently working in an engineering field</li>
    <li>have a <strong>technical interest</strong> and want to learn more</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mb-10 leading-relaxed">Whatever your background or engineering experience, the majority of this course will be useful for you to get the best out of your future, in a remarkably useful way.</p>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">How It's Taught</h2>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">The course is delivered by us through live seminars, so that we can come back and add to your understanding in person if needed for a number of weeks, but we can set the time to suit your preference.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">All sessions will be hosted online, so you can stay at your home or office, and we'll continue our 1-on-1 with you over a couple of sessions, but we can set the date to suit your preference.</p>

  <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">At the end of the course, you'll receive a customised set of notes for both your work and reference, and we'll continue to support you with future learning, opportunities to get yourself started in the industry.</p>

  <a href="/contact" class="inline-block border border-(--color-border) px-6 py-2 text-sm no-underline hover:border-(--color-accent) hover:text-(--color-accent) transition-colors mb-12">Reach out →</a>

  <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-10 mt-10 mb-6">
    <div class="max-w-[560px]">
      <div class="aspect-video w-full">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nG00PeG00IQ"
          class="w-full h-full"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen
          title="Learn with us: Vehicle Dynamics Fundamentals Course II">
        </iframe>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm" style="color:rgba(0,0,0,0.45);">Learn with us: Vehicle Dynamics Fundamentals Course II — director's introduction to the course.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</ArticleLayout>
